name: WODMode
0:
”Alexa, ask Wod Mode what is today's workout”
”Alexa, ask Wod Mode what's my schedule”
”Alexa, ask Wod Mode to sign me up for Monday Five AM Class”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: wod mode
des: Have you ever layed in bed and wondered what crazy WOD was planned for today....but checking it out on your phone means opening your eyes? Problem solved, call out "Alexa, ask Wod Mode for today's workout". You can register for class using our MINDBODY integration....or shame on you, cancel a class because of a hangover. But be sure to do it with at least one hours notice ;)
